a tub of hummus, but thanks.

15:44.247 --> 15:45.901
Ah, o-okay.

15:45.945 --> 15:47.729
Well, okay,
here's the thing.

15:47.772 --> 15:48.991
Um...

15:49.035 --> 15:53.343
