you country bumpkin.

17:15.686 --> 17:19.734
Oh, well, um, I'm sorry,
I-I didn't know, I...

17:20.996 --> 17:23.390
Well, since you didn't eat it,
I guess...

17:23.433 --> 17:25.392
I'll just make you
eat your words.

17:29.744 --> 17:31.659
Andi.

17:31.702 --> 17:34.618
Maybe you did
pull that kitten's leg off.

17:36.707 --> 17:40.494
