I did a good job apologizing.

18:00.079 --> 18:02.342
But I knew
you couldn't resist

18:02.385 --> 18:04.083
rubbing it in
once I caved.

18:04.126 --> 18:06.215
People don't change.

18:06.259 --> 18:08.391
I wear white socks
when you go out of town.

18:10.219 --> 18:12.091
Adam Burns for the win.

18:13.222 --> 18:14.876
Yeah, that's right.
You may have fooled me,

18:14.919 --> 18:17.313
but the man I married is
pathologically suspicious

18:17.357 --> 18:19.837
and sometimes
that comes in handy.
Mm-hmm.

18:19.881 --> 18:22.536
