18:22.579 --> 18:25.191
I was just trying to make
you eat it 'cause it's expired.

18:26.757 --> 18:28.933
Now everyone
will believe me.

18:28.977 --> 18:31.022
And-- Wait.
Where's Don and Marcy?

18:31.066 --> 18:32.937
