have to be in here?

18:39.553 --> 18:40.858
I don't know.

18:40.902 --> 18:42.599
Adam just said
wait in the pantry.

18:50.607 --> 18:52.696
Lowell, we're sorry Kelly's
not who you thought she was.

18:52.740 --> 18:55.351
Thank you.Yeah.

18:55.395 --> 18:58.311
Maybe during this difficult
time, you'll find some comfort

18:58.354 --> 19:00.530
